Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:29.10,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(130,130)}彼方的假日·梳發
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.94,0:24:14.85,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 蟬時雨·精靈流
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.46,0:02:11.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…計畫是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.69,0:02:12.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.93,0:02:14.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始作戰…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:16.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出門嗎 小彼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.95,0:02:21.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:24.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就用你的第一份薪餉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:25.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是用全部哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.06,0:02:30.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會寄錢回鄉下 順便想送點禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:31.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:32.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獎勵一下自己嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:34.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:38.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初的一個月是見習所以沒有薪餉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.41,0:02:40.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高興死你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:42.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不過我嚇一跳了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.06,0:02:48.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說薪餉誤期是理所當然\N一般都是給軍票的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:51.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.16,0:02:55.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.68,0:03:01.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真沒想過能順利領到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:03.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.29,0:03:05.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的部隊可是為此特地去搞副業…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.28,0:03:10.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方 那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:13.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天市場開了 你是第一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.73,0:03:18.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初薪加初假 小彼跟「初」字真有緣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:21.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記正業 好好去放鬆一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:23.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:33.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:44.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了不要讓彼方察覺到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:52.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 用常識想一想\N在這樣邊遠地區怎麼可能如期發薪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:04:01.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方還那麼輕易就相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:04.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,率直就是小彼的優點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:10.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟馬上就懷疑錢的出處的你們不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:12.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:17.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:22.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我們也忘記正業吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:31.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.59,0:04:32.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.69,0:04:34.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過有一個問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:37.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我再打折可沒門哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.48,0:04:45.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起 我太入神了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.47,0:04:59.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:01.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一切沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:05.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊出問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:10.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個提案 要做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.01,0:05:13.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能詳細說說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:20.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的也很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.89,0:05:39.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:42.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西的賣主就是你們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:52.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,商品合你心意了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:53.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:59.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 有個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:01.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 是什麼問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:03.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要處理這個數量的商品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:06.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,費門路又花工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.77,0:06:10.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一考慮到這個 錢就不太夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:11.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.65,0:06:13.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜歡打折扣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:16.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,價錢可是恰到好處的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.95,0:06:20.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會要你打折
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:24.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全收下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:26.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:33.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想開槍就開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.61,0:06:37.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 在那之前這傢伙會冒出火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:40.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次會幫你天靈蓋開個通風洞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:42.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:46.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:54.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是小看我們的下場
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:57.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安 小弟弟們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:30.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就說了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:35.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:39.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也和那些傢伙一夥的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.68,0:07:45.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:54.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我們的車
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:56.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:07:58.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:01.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 給首領的禮物…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:02.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命子要緊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:04.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭兒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:06.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不知道 那是群危險的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:09.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以後也不來這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:15.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:17.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:21.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那沒事了 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.47,0:08:25.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真讓我捏了一把汗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.07,0:08:28.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來騙到他們了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.52,0:08:31.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝協助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:36.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 要是中央的黑手黨混過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:38.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也不好做生意了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:41.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相幫助…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:42.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:46.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們幫你做這齣戲 當然會有點打賞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:48.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:51.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麥克爾先生 老是給我開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:55.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不不 不是開玩笑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:57.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是生意的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:09:01.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.55,0:09:05.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的他們的車 是你們弄的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:08.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你弄的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.10,0:09:09.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.49,0:09:12.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:15.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是誰把車弄得散架了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:21.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡面 有好些在市場上四處搜購的戰備品
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:26.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我買下 利潤平分 如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:30.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買賣成立呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:32.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:37.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這把戲終於搞完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.06,0:09:39.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我真有點吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:40.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃驚什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:45.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 梨旺前輩興致勃勃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:47.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私釀這些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:50.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果穿幫了 可不僅僅是上軍事法庭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.10,0:09:56.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,違反專賣法和稅法 最高均可判叛國罪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:10:00.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 雖然是從前輩那繼承下來的副業
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:03.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨旺一次也沒有反對過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:05.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也感到有點意外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.62,0:10:15.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始當然吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.95,0:10:22.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我知道 媽媽曾經喜歡的卡巴度斯\N竟然是在要塞裡釀造的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.15,0:10:26.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你能分配到這個部隊來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.03,0:10:30.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是你媽媽指引的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:50.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:11:00.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由美奈姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:03.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了 看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.02,0:11:06.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好看哦 誠也
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.83,0:11:17.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美汐 今天是初入禮拜的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:21.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭司也在 所以今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:22.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:27.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓姐姐為難啊 美汐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.73,0:11:29.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係 就梳一梳頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.01,0:11:31.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.03,0:11:35.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 平時還嚷著要梳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:36.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠也真煩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.87,0:11:43.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以這樣的 美汐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.57,0:11:48.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美汐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:55.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10圓25分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:01.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危險的啊 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:04.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起 我太入神了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:07.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:09.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題就是他們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:12.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來被他們探出我們的交易
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:18.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.87,0:12:21.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 直美姐～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.10,0:12:24.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.65,0:12:28.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我錢包裡第一次有能買下這個的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.03,0:12:32.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在跟你說「我要這個」的話 就能買下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:36.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 如果有人想跟你爭這只海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:37.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.13,0:12:41.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人想要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:44.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是打個比方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:47.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:48.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:52.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 跟他說海豚是吃人的可怕的動物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:53.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他死心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.94,0:12:57.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你真是天才
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:12:59.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那只海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:03.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到你不要為止 我會一直幫你留住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.31,0:13:04.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你繼續苦惱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:09.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 先決定好給大家的禮物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.48,0:13:20.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 爸爸 媽媽 爺爺 奶奶\N瓦倫的爺爺 奶奶 最後是曾奶奶…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.64,0:13:23.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有隔壁的七惠婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:30.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害 有賣各種的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.56,0:13:31.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:33.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:38.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 小美？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:40.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要買什麼東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:43.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是在找盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:44.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盒子？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:48.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的 在哪見過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:52.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:58.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.72,0:14:01.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方 你在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:04.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在買禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:08.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道有沒有能送給鄉下家人的好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.79,0:14:10.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我不急…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:10.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要你幫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:23.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了呢 小美…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:30.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個畢竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:32.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是件漂亮的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:35.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件也很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.09,0:14:40.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由美奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.59,0:14:43.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:45.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有見到美汐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:49.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盒子？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:52.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:54.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:15:01.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她媽媽去世的時候 家產全到了別人手裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:07.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是在那時候被奪走的媽媽的遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:12.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她每當開市場的日子 都去碰碰運氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:17.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了些不好的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.46,0:15:21.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天 第一次領到薪餉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.83,0:15:24.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我說 給家人送禮物…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.92,0:15:26.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:32.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為現在我…我們就是美汐的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.97,0:15:36.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果美汐還覺得嫉妒的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:41.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都是因為我做得不夠周到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.56,0:15:55.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:58.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽的這個寶盒和我 哪個更重要？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:00.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.20,0:16:07.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.51,0:16:15.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:26.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:34.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來看 托雷茲的名產鞭炮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:34.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}托雷茲：Treize，法語的13
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.08,0:16:36.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,響得很好聽的 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:45.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…由美奈姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:47.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:48.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:56.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我們的車
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:05.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我不是由美奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:14.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…由美奈姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.08,0:17:16.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:17.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:23.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:24.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.22,0:17:29.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…哎呀 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.99,0:17:33.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道 那輛車…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.77,0:17:35.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是直美姐的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:37.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那難道是你們弄的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:40.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.38,0:17:42.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 這裡有150圓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.34,0:17:44.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我賠…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.19,0:17:47.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幹得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:49.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把錢好好收起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:52.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢我已經收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:17:59.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直…直美姐 那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.29,0:18:07.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是美麗的稻穗的伊狄亞文字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:09.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個刻在印章上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:14.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子一定會過上如農田豐收般幸福的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:18.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美穗 能夠得到個好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:20.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.92,0:18:28.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到美汐了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.99,0:18:35.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了成為她的家人 我自問已經費盡心思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.95,0:18:38.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還差得很遠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:42.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:47.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美汐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.29,0:18:55.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 找到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:57.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好珍惜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:00.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無以替代的媽媽的回憶…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.01,0:19:01.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:07.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想請由美奈收下這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:20.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美汐是失去家人後被教會接養的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.25,0:19:26.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先是父親出征 一去不返
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.99,0:19:27.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:34.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美汐的家人住在西邊國境--維倫丹特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.30,0:19:35.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:39.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就是住在那個\N被看不見的死神襲擊的城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:43.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後她們兩人來到賽茲的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:47.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她母親就已經發生症狀 不久後便…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:52.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽她說過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.01,0:19:56.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我不定幫你梳頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:58.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢 然後說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:04.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後就讓最珍視美汐的人幫你梳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.69,0:20:08.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由美奈幫我梳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:16.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人要活著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.12,0:20:22.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使與重要的人永別\N在那時候感到死一般的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:27.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 我們也要活著 活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.21,0:20:32.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份堅強 是多麼的悲傷 多麼的可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:39.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.68,0:20:41.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.03,0:20:55.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在洗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.96,0:20:57.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我馬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.59,0:21:03.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:07.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 可以的話我也盡量不想洗頭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.19,0:21:09.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過發生很多事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:11.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.21,0:21:14.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼前輩 請讓我幫你擦頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:16.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很想摸一摸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:23.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最後還是沒買那海豚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:27.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你給自己的獎勵是那海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.53,0:21:33.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨旺前輩相信命運嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.05,0:21:35.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 突然說這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.25,0:21:40.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得呢 今天發生了些事讓我想到這個
